did.unittitle: Annual Honors Day and other event programs

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: Includes program for a Modern Dance Recital: Presenation of Intramural Awards, May 26, 1942; program for the Annual Spring Concert, May 25, 1961; program for a production of Stage Door, undated; and programs (photocopies) for Annual Honors Day, 1958-1961.
